{
  "stem": "19518.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 310.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it was a camp for girls and youngsters, and I was one of the older children then.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was very hard to get onto the train, because they were transporting the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] army people to and fro.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was very hard-- and besides, it was very hard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "People were running.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They did not know where to.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But many more people were running.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We could hardly make it to Cracow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "A trip that was, under normal conditions on that train, took three to four hours.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It took over a night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I final-- we, we got-- we reached our-- I reached my home towards, I think, August 30.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we started our trek-- we walked to the station instead of having transportation, because there was none anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then it was very hard to get on that-- on the train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We held on for dear life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Standing room was like sardines, but we finally made it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I arrived home with whatever I had on my back.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the luggage already we could not retrieve.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And a day or two later, the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- I recall it was 7 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At 6 o'clock, a bang woke us all up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was already on the way to shul.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He came back, and he said that the war broke out, that the Germans bombed the station in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lived quite far away from the station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we heard the bang.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the one and only time that Cracow was bombarded.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Dietlowska.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "D-I-E-T-L-O-W-S-K-A.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was the outskirts of the Jewish quarter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was an area, I don't know if you've heard of [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
